This directory contains a trimmed copy of source files from the VGN project:

  Volumetric Grasping Network (VGN)
  https://github.com/ethz-asl/vgn
  Copyright (c) 2020, ETHZ ASL
  Licensed under the BSD 3-Clause License (see LICENSE)

Files included (inference only, unmodified except where noted):
  __init__.py, detection.py, grasp.py, networks.py, utils/transform.py

Modifications:
  detection.py — moved `from vgn import vis` import inside the `if self.rviz:`
  branch to avoid a transitive dependency on ROS sensor_msgs when running
  outside a ROS environment.

Reference:
  M. Breyer, J. J. Chung, L. Ott, R. Siegwart, and J. Nieto,
  "Volumetric Grasping Network: Real-time 6 DOF Grasp Detection in Clutter",
  Conference on Robot Learning (CoRL), 2020.
